isc models of the velocity and velocity dispersion\nfield to correct for beam smearing. The corrected flux-weighted velocity\ndispersion values are sigma_m~20-50 km/s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 1 Feb 2016 22:57:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 Feb 2016 04:38:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
