 where\nthe mathematical analysis is applicable, numerical examples that illustrate the\ntheoretical results are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Feb 2016 09:39:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Mar 2016 11:45:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2017 14:33:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-23"}
