retching to provide a qualitative picture via the tip vortices of\nthe physics of blade ventilation in surface piercing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Feb 2016 12:19:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Feb 2019 10:41:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-14"}
